gui.version.title=Announcement
gui.version.tab.text1=New Items added
gui.version.title.text1=Super fun new Items are here!
gui.version.content.text1=▢FFF0A12FDear Warriors,\\n▢FFF0A12FWe added a lot of new Items, and a small number of weapons, equipment, the specific new content as listed below.\\n▢FFFFFFFF1. Power crossbow: damage: 5, knockback: 2, a very good long-range weapon\\n2. Ice shoes: turn the surrounding destructible blocks into ice blocks\\n3. Ninja shoes: +1 jump, no fall damage\\n4. Water ball: Could be thrown, and turns into a pool of water when hits the ground\\n5. Bridge egg (new): Generate a bridge when thrown\\n6. Shadow Dragon Scroll: Summon the shadow dragon for you to ride, shooting flame balls constantly and you can break blocks when you hit them \\n7. Retrospective pearl: Take you to the target place after you threwn, and teleport back after 6 seconds\\n8. Paragliding: When you fall into the void you will be brought back high and glide for a while\\n9. Disguised Bomb: Place a Landmine, it will explode when enemies passed by\\n10. Frozen Trap: Place an invisible trap, freeze the enemies who passed by \\n11. Detector: Place a radar and will inform you when there are enemies passed by\\n12. Double puppet: Place a puppet, it can get the resources for you. You get a button to teleport back to where the puppet was placed.  \\n13. Fishing Rod:  You can pull the enemies you hooked back, a medium-ranged weapon\\n
