gui.version.tab.text2=Update 1.1
gui.version.title.text2=Experience optimization
gui.version.content.text2=▢FFF0A12F Dear warrior: \\n▢FFF0A12F We have made some experience optimizations: \\n▢FFFFFFFF1. Team system: Now teaming is more convenient, and you can invite strangers to play together! \\n2.Chat system: Now you can join other people's team on the chat interface, you can express love, and you can chat with players on other servers! \\n3. Friend System: Now it is more convenient to add friends, and the follow function is added, you can follow the players you like! \\n4. Personal homepage: a new personal homepage, you can view your own or other people's information\\n5. Skin fragments: Now all skin fragments have been converted to general fragments, which can be used to redeem more skins!
